@node 256  ""
@toc AmigaFront6.guide/main

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------

    D-GENERATION:

	Shifra za kompjuter je "DEATH".

	Kada  poginesh, vrti dzhojstik u  krug drzheci pritisnuto pucanje.
	Zapochecesh igru na mestu na kom si poginuo i imacesh 7-8 zhivota.

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node 257  ""
@toc AmigaFront6.guide/main

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------

    D-GENERATION CD32:

	Upishi  "SETH" kao user name na prvom kompjuteru. Upishi "OSTRICH"
	kao pass name. Na drugom kompjuteru upishi "DEATH" kao user name i
	aktiviracesh cheat mod.

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node 258 ""
@toc AmigaFront6.guide/main

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------

    *DALEK ATTACK:

	Kada dodjesh u London upishi neshto od sledeceg:

         PARIS---"DAY OF RECKONING"        TOKYO---"TRICOLOUR COFFEE SHOP"
         NEW YORK-----"THE SLYTHER"        SKARO--------"D5 GAMMA Z ALPHA"


                               Nevidljivost
              "JAMES BOND AND OLIVER REED WERE NEVER GOOD SINGERS"

                              Bezbroj zhivota
         "TRUE I AM GUILTY OF INTERFERENCE JUST AS YOU ARE GUILTY 
                  OF FAILING  TO USE YOUR GREAT POWERS" 

                                    ???
                              "ESCAPE SWITCH"

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node 259 ""
@toc AmigaFront6.guide/main

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------

    DALEY THOMPSON OLYMPIC CHALLENGE:

	Na high score tabeli upishi "HINGSEN.J" kao svoje ime.  Discipline
	birash funkcijskim tasterima.

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node 261 ""
@toc AmigaFront6.guide/main

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------

    DAMOCLES:

        Na Midas koordinatama 577-341 mozes naci piramidu koja sadrzi
        magicni kristal. Da bi ga iskoristio treba ti kniga koju mozes
        naci u Eris glavnom gradu (13-5). Citaj knjigu dok si u posedu
        kristala i ispunice ti se jedna od sledecih zelja:

                I WISH I HAD A CHEESE SANDWICH
                I WISH I HAD MORE TIME
                I WISH I COULD RECIEVE 1,000,000 CREDITS
                I WISH THE UNIVERSE WAS MORE COLOURFUL
                I WISH I KNOW HOW TO USE AUTHOR'S COMPUTER
                I WISH I HAD MERCENARY 3 NOW

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node 262 ""
@toc AmigaFront6.guide/main

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------

    *DARK CASTLE:

        Prva stvar koju treba da uradis je da odes u sobu sa stitivima.
        Pritisni po jednom 'W' (gore) i 'S' (dole). Drzi ih oba pritisnuta.
        Ovo ce prouzrokovati da tvoj junak otici gore i dole izmedju 2
	ekrana, a ti ces dobiti 25 zivota. Ovo mozes uraditi samo u sobi
	sa stitovima.

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node 263 ""
@toc AmigaFront6.guide/main

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------

    *DARKMAN:

	Upishi "MEA CULPA" u toku igre i koristi sledece tastere:

             'I'                                  nevidljivost
             'Z'                  ubija neprijatelje na ekranu
             'D'                                           ???
             'P'                             popunjava zhivote
             'R'                                           ???
             'SPACE'                                       ???
             '1'-'6'              odlazak na odgovarajuci nivo
             'F1'-'F7'            odlazak na odgovarajuci nivo
             'F8'                      odlazak na sledeci nivo
             'J'                                           ???
                        
     ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
@node 264 ""
@toc AmigaFront6.guide/main

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------

    *DARKSIDE:

	Da bi video slike programera, srzhi pritisnute tastere '2' i '8' i
	na glavnoj i na numerichkoj tastaturi.

     ----------------------------------------------------------------------
@endnode
